### Verify Order Delivery with Code
POST http://localhost:3003/api/orders/501/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "verificationCode": "ABC123"
}

### Expected Response (200 OK)
# {
#   "message": "Order verified successfully",
#   "order": {
#     "orderId": 501,
#     "status": "DELIVERED",
#     "deliveredAt": "2025-06-19T15:28:00.000Z"
#   }
# }

### Submit Order Rating and Feedback
POST http://localhost:3003/api/orders/501/rating
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent service and delicious food!",
  "restaurantRating": 5,
  "deliveryPersonRating": 5
}

### Expected Response (200 OK)
